metadata.name: GEN XYZ Das Occult #1681
metadata.description:
A 10k Generative Profile Pic collection
GEN XYZ Das Occult - by culla - @tamccullough

move over cryptopunks
there is a new group on the scene

100% code - not an image composition

A bunch of common palettes
A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes
However, rarity will be based on what combinations the code produces

The majority of tokens will not have a special trait
However your token might have one or even multiple special traits
But, be aware that only the last special trait added will be listed in the features

Even then, look closely, because not all aspects of the canvas are included in the features. Collectors should still look closely and choose what they like when buying on secondary.

Which team are you on? X or O?

follow culla on twitter for updates. Or maybe __acolyte__

If the non reserved tokens mint out quickly, Access List mints will have 24 hours to mint reserves assigned to those wallets

Thank you for supporting an emerging artist in the generative art space

Access List reserves were given to holders of the following PFP collections created by culla
2x for each Basqunk held
1x for each Inkspunk, TwoFourQunk, V0iD, DeeManz, Punkasso and CR0$$KULL
You would have needed to transfer the above tokens to your mint wallet at the time of the snapshot

share your tokens on social media with #genxyznft
Made with love by culla using p5.js

metadata.name: Gammalt #339
metadata.description:
Celebrating getting old with Fx(hash).

Save as png:
Click “s”
or double click/tap

Resolution:
Default image width = 2000px and aspect ratio = 4:3.
Modify the image width between 2000px and 10000px by adding “&w=xxxx” to the url (e.g. &w=4000).
High resolutions are computationally expensive and may take a while.

Background:
The canvas background texture is visible by default. This can be toggled off by adding “&b=0” to the url.
The background scales with resolution to mimic a bigger canvas so it will look different at different resolutions.
At high resolutions a Moiré pattern may appear on the canvas background texture due to the way images are resized in the browser. It’s always recommended to download a full resolution version of the piece.

By KRANKARTA
Created on Firefox desktop 105.0 on 2022-11-11 in javascript and GLSL.
CC BY-NC-ND 4.0

metadata.name: Vertical World #60
metadata.description:
This artwork is a kind of my inquiry about ambiguous boundaries.
I was a child who liked to draw but always been dissatisfied with my work. Now through coding, I was able to create the "feelings" that I wanted to express. This work is not to imitate a certain landscape or painting style, but simply paint with different brushes, and cooperate with the randomness of the computer.
"I" creates horizontal order, and "computer" creates vertical disorder. My intention is to create
ambiguous visuals in a way that doesn't give specific images, but vague atmosphere.
The meaning is computer-generated and positioned through your eyes.
(It may take more time to render if you using Firefox browser.)

- Press [s] to save png image

Created by haxenfan using p5js.

metadata.name: System α #149
metadata.description:
"To capture the fleeting time in the generating process."

In this work,I d'like focus on the generating of generative art system itself rather than imitate some scene or style.
And with the flow of time, try to figure out where it can take me toward.

This work would be a series of my alternative view on generative art.
"α" means the first step of this series.

Press [s] in live view to save file as PNG.
Press [p] to stop.

------
Happy first birthday fx(hash) !!

20% of primary revenues go to Savepakistan Flood Relief Fundraiser.
20% of primary revenues go to the Processing foundation.

metadata.name: 🟧🟦 QT 🟦🟧 #255
metadata.description:
🟧🟦 Qt is a unique interactive PFP.

🔶As you move the mouse, QT eyes monitor your movements and react accordingly. If you're lucky enough to have laser eyes, you have a QT protecting you. There are several gift hearts and diamonds around you that you can pick up(There is no doubt that you will use them somewhere.). Your QTs bring nouns and behavioral adjectives with them. In the gift that's going around the platform, you'll find it.

A total of thirty rare groups are considered for QTs, making them unique among PFPs and allowing you to have diverse and exclusive QTs.

🔷QT is not just an NFT. To make significant events more enjoyable, QT is with you. All you need to do is own QTs and follow them. You will be surprised by QTs. 1011 girls and 1011 boys will mint in the first series of QTs in 2022. At the opening of the 2022 World Cup, the first QT Boy pieces were minted.

🤝Saleh.C4d and  ArashMP collaborated on QT.

✅ you can save the image in the following sizes:

⌨️ Key number 1️⃣ 1080 pixels

metadata.name: Color Field Starry B #147
metadata.description:
Look up at the stars, knowing our own small.
Pure color and simplified abstraction bring the release of the spirit and the collision of the emotions.In fact, it is to excavate the emotional activity from the heart of hearts and convey the basic feelings of human beings.
The separation of colors is like the bond of the Creator's heart,connecting sadness, anger, sorrow and joy.
If large-scale color is completely emotional, the stars represent the spark of thoughts.
We hope that the audience and the works establish a direct and intimate sensory contact, experience the rhythm of color, feel the image of almost completely abstract, non-theme of the uncertain form.

50% of secondary market royalties go to minters.

Twitter: @lilyaaanaaa
Release in 2022

Made with p5.js

metadata.name: Chroma-Curves #7
metadata.description:
Each output is generated by layering Blender renders.

'Chroma-Curves' is inspired by mid-century modern minimalist art.

Each output consists of curves and circles on a colored background. The scale of the various components coupled with the carefully balanced colors create a bold, striking geometric design.

In live mode:
Click/tap the image to make a "Download image" button appear. Click this button to download a 1500x2000px PNG.
